  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Printing the header and footer of a page is determined by your browser settings. If you want to remove the header and footer and only print the ticket content, you will need to remove them on your print page settings.</p><h3 id=\"RemovingtheHeaderandFooterDetailsWhenPrintingReceipts-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361958/Print+Settings+-+Receipt+Template\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361958\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Receipts</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936851011/Add+a+Qsite+Ticket+Status+Link+to+Receipts+and+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936851011\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Adding a Qsite\u2122 Ticket Status Link to Receipts</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933279270/Add+Your+Logo+to+Receipts+and+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933279270\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Add Your Logo to Receipts and Invoices</a>  </p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RemovingtheHeaderandFooterDetailsWhenPrintingReceipts-GoogleChrome\">Google Chrome</h2><p>When viewing the print dialog box, uncheck the option for Headers and Footers.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%201.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RemovingtheHeaderandFooterDetailsWhenPrintingReceipts-Firefox\">Firefox</h2><p>1. Click the Options button on the right side of the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. From the list of options, click <strong>Print</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"226\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. On the Print Settings page, scroll down and uncheck the box next to <strong>Print Headers and Footers</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"RemovingtheHeaderandFooterDetailsWhenPrintingReceipts-Safari\">Safari</h2><p>1. Print the ticket using the Browser Dialog option.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. In the print dialog box, uncheck the box next to <strong>Print Headers and Footers</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%206.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"RemovingtheHeaderandFooterDetailsWhenPrintingReceipts-MicrosoftEdge\">Microsoft Edge</h2><p>1. Click the Options button on the right side of the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. From the list of options, click <strong>Print</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"226\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%208.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. On the Print Settings page scroll down and expand the <strong>More Settings</strong> section. Uncheck the box next to <strong>Headers and Footers</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"226\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933541617/Header%209.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
